

Keywords:
		Search keywords:  method operator	
 
Technical content:
		Title: 	 method operator improvements	     	
		Objective: To know the method operator improvements in 2009.12		
		Description: The following are the method operator Improvements done  
		
string str.getc(index) and str[index] consistency 
Support for enum type in conditional operator 
allow void casting of system-tasks 
modport for virtual interface 
Call a method on an object returned from a class method
Assignments in expressions made more robust 
Function named arguments
Better $stack support 
$exit 
Pure virtual function/task
 
		
		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	comp            -- To compile the design
        run             -- To run the design
        all             -- It does all the above steps.
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 
